00:32:47.020 --> 00:32:50.630
The third step in
The Babyproof Method

00:32:50.630 --> 00:32:53.720
is to practice the skills.

00:32:53.720 --> 00:32:55.340
Think of David.

00:32:55.340 --> 00:32:58.975
He didn't show up to face
Goliath ready to throw

00:32:58.975 --> 00:33:00.965
a slingshot for the first time.

00:33:00.965 --> 00:33:03.850
It takes practice
to become an expert.

00:33:03.850 --> 00:33:06.650
And the good thing is,
if you do practice,

00:33:06.650 --> 00:33:09.390
you will become an expert.

00:33:09.390 --> 00:33:12.230
So the practice step is
all about looking at,

00:33:12.230 --> 00:33:14.330
