convince himself to keep going,

00:34:18.219 --> 00:34:20.040
to keep trying?

00:34:20.040 --> 00:34:23.250
Victor Frankl, how does
he, despite everyday

00:34:23.250 --> 00:34:25.176
all the evidence
to the contrary,

00:34:25.176 --> 00:34:29.610
convince himself that it's worth
fighting for, to keep going?

00:34:32.440 --> 00:34:36.269
Picture, practice, prepare.

00:34:36.269 --> 00:34:40.920
Picture, prepare,
practice, persevere.

