00:37:27.300 --> 00:37:31.130
Getting up early is a
controllable for everybody.

00:37:31.130 --> 00:37:34.346
Let me tell you just three
of the many reasons why

00:37:34.346 --> 00:37:36.512
for me, it's one of the
most important controllables

00:37:36.512 --> 00:37:38.690
in my life.

00:37:38.690 --> 00:37:41.970
The first one is it
gives me me time.

00:37:41.970 --> 00:37:47.255
That essential time
at a time in the day--

00:37:47.255 --> 00:37:50.860
in fact, the only time in the
day over which I could have

00:37:50.860 --> 00:37:52.240
control.

00:37:52.240 --> 00:37:57.210
It means even if that me time
is 10 minutes, 15 minutes,

00:37:57.210 --> 00:38:01.290
I have time to think about
myself in a way that prepares

00:38:01.290 --> 00:38:04.950
and allows me to be
available for everybody

00:38:04.950 --> 00:38:07.350
else for the rest of the day.

00:38:07.350 --> 00:38:09.840
It is a me time
that is so sacred,

00:38:09.840 --> 00:38:12.780
that on the odd occasion
where I think, oh, I'll

00:38:12.780 --> 00:38:16.170
lie in tomorrow, that
voice my head says,

00:38:16.170 --> 00:38:18.610
how could you do that to me?

00:38:18.610 --> 00:38:23.995
How could you take away the
most important bit of my day?

00:38:23.995 --> 00:38:26.650
You can ask my husband,
it drives him mad.

00:38:26.650 --> 00:38:30.210
I have got to the point where
it's so beneficial to me,

00:38:30.210 --> 00:38:34.080
I'm almost incapable
of lying in.

00:38:34.080 --> 00:38:37.350
It is so powerful
and important to me.

00:38:37.350 --> 00:38:39.600
The second reason
is it's a moment

00:38:39.600 --> 00:38:44.190
in the day, everyday, where
I can have perspective

00:38:44.190 --> 00:38:47.320
on that day, on my week.

00:38:47.320 --> 00:38:51.630
I can look with some distance
and say, what's working?

00:38:51.630 --> 00:38:52.800
What am I doing today?

00:38:52.800 --> 00:38:55.260
What have I been doing in
the last few weeks that's

00:38:55.260 --> 00:38:57.720
working well for me,
that's making me feel good

00:38:57.720 --> 00:39:00.030
like I'm in control?

00:39:00.030 --> 00:39:02.120
And what's not working?

00:39:02.120 --> 00:39:04.570
What is it that
I need to change?

00:39:04.570 --> 00:39:07.020
And it gives me that
moment of reflection

00:39:07.020 --> 00:39:10.200
to come up with solutions, to
come up with different things

00:39:10.200 --> 00:39:11.070
to try.

00:39:11.070 --> 00:39:17.530
And trust me, you create the
space for solutions and ideas.

00:39:17.530 --> 00:39:19.030
Hey, that's what
you guys do here,

00:39:19.030 --> 00:39:23.310
we create space for
ideas for innovation.

00:39:23.310 --> 00:39:28.600
You will come up with solutions,
different things to try.

00:39:28.600 --> 00:39:30.290
And the third and
final reason, it

00:39:30.290 --> 00:39:34.230
helps to keep me connected
with the big picture.

00:39:34.230 --> 00:39:36.020
So hard to remember
the big picture

00:39:36.020 --> 00:39:40.420
when you're busy all the
time, completely working hard,

00:39:40.420 --> 00:39:44.330
overwhelmed, being stretched
from one task to the next.

00:39:44.330 --> 00:39:46.650
The big picture is just the why.

00:39:46.650 --> 00:39:48.020
Why are you doing this?

00:39:48.020 --> 00:39:49.670
Why do you have a family?

00:39:49.670 --> 00:39:51.080
Why do you care?

00:39:51.080 --> 00:39:53.784
Why are you still working when
you know that you would also

00:39:53.784 --> 00:39:54.950
like to be with your family?

00:39:54.950 --> 00:39:56.285
What does work give you?

00:39:56.285 --> 00:39:59.730
And connecting with
that on a regular basis

00:39:59.730 --> 00:40:02.420
makes all the difference when I
turn around to my six-year-old

00:40:02.420 --> 00:40:05.220
and I say, I can't
come to this event

00:40:05.220 --> 00:40:09.962
today because mommy's got to
go and do this piece of work.

00:40:09.962 --> 00:40:11.920
But don't worry, when I
see you at the weekend,

00:40:11.920 --> 00:40:14.750
we'll do X, Y, and
Z. And I do not

00:40:14.750 --> 00:40:18.200
feel guilty about
the number of things

00:40:18.200 --> 00:40:23.350
that I say no to, because in
my head always is a compass,

00:40:23.350 --> 00:40:27.410
is the big picture, is the
life I want for my children,

00:40:27.410 --> 00:40:30.960
for my family, and for myself.

00:40:30.960 --> 00:40:34.795
There are just three of many
reasons why getting up early

00:40:34.795 --> 00:40:37.530
is such a powerful
controllable feeling.

00:40:37.530 --> 00:40:41.210
And I want you to
experiment with it yourself.

